Should they be included in the resampling and caching workflow?

Are they legacy/unwanted pages that should be excluded?

If they should be shown, which category or section should they belong to?

Clarifying this will allow us to finalize the ingestion pipeline and ensure we only display relevant content.

Please let me know your thoughts on both the caching recommendation and how we should handle these unmapped articles.

